<h2>
  <svg style="display: inline-block; width: 32px; height: 32px; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 8px;" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
    <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
  </svg>
  Pedido Confirmado!
</h2>
<p>Olá, <strong style="color: #3F51B5;">{{nomeUsuario}}</strong>!</p>
<p style="font-size: 17px;">Seu pedido foi confirmado e está sendo processado. Você pode visualizar todos os detalhes abaixo. <strong style="color: #4CAF50;">Obrigado pela sua compra!</strong></p>
<div class="info-box" style="border-left-color: #2196F3; background: rgba(33, 150, 243, 0.1);">
  <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px;">
    <svg style="width: 24px; height: 24px; color: #3F51B5;" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
      <path d="M16 11V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4M5 9h14l1 12H4L5 9z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
    </svg>
    <p style="margin: 0;">
      <strong style="color: #333333;">Número do Pedido:</strong> 
      <span style="color: #2196F3; font-weight: 700; font-size: 17px;">#{{orderNumber}}</span>
    </p>
  </div>
  <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;">
    <svg style="width: 24px; height: 24px; color: #3F51B5;" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
      <path d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
    </svg>
    <p style="margin: 0;">
      <strong style="color: #333333;">Data do Pedido:</strong> 
      <span style="color: #555555;">{{orderDate}}</span>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div style="margin: 32px 0;">
  <h3 style="color: #3F51B5; font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(63, 81, 181, 0.3); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
    <svg style="width: 24px; height: 24px; color: #3F51B5;" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
      <path d="M3 3h2l.4 2M7 13h10l4-8H5.4M7 13L5.4 5M7 13l-2.293 2.293c-.63.63-.184 1.707.707 1.707H17m0 0a2 2 0 100 4 2 2 0 000-4zm-8 2a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
    </svg>
    Itens do Pedido
  </h3>
  
  <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
    <thead>
      <tr style="background: rgba(63, 81, 181, 0.1); border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(63, 81, 181, 0.3);">
        <th style="padding: 14px 12px; text-align: left; font-size: 14px; color: #3F51B5; font-weight: 600;">Item</th>
        <th style="padding: 14px 12px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: #3F51B5; width: 80px; font-weight: 600;">Qtd</th>
        <th style="padding: 14px 12px; text-align: right; font-size: 14px; color: #3F51B5; width: 120px; font-weight: 600;">Preço</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      {{#each items}}
      <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(63, 81, 181, 0.15);">
        <td style="padding: 14px 12px; font-size: 15px; color: #555555;">{{this.name}}</td>
        <td style="padding: 14px 12px; text-align: center; font-size: 15px; color: #555555;">{{this.quantity}}</td>
        <td style="padding: 14px 12px; text-align: right; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: #3F51B5;">{{formatCurrency this.price}}</td>
      </tr>
      {{/each}}
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <table style="width: 100%; margin-top: 24px;">
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 10px 12px; font-size: 15px; color: #555555; width: 70%;">Subtotal:</td>
      <td style="padding: 10px 12px; text-align: right; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: #555555;">{{formatCurrency subtotal}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 10px 12px; font-size: 15px; color: #555555;">Frete:</td>
      <td style="padding: 10px 12px; text-align: right; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: #555555;">{{formatCurrency shipping}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 10px 12px 20px 12px; font-size: 15px; color: #555555; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgba(63, 81, 181, 0.3);">Impostos:</td>
      <td style="padding: 10px 12px 20px 12px; text-align: right; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: #555555; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgba(63, 81, 181, 0.3);">{{formatCurrency tax}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr style="background: rgba(63, 81, 181, 0.1);">
      <td style="padding: 16px 12px; font-size: 19px; font-weight: 700; color: #3F51B5;">Total:</td>
      <td style="padding: 16px 12px; text-align: right; font-size: 19px; font-weight: 700; color: #2196F3;">{{formatCurrency total}}</td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</div>
<div class="info-box" style="border-left-color: #3F51B5; background: #F3F5FC;">
  <p style="margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #3F51B5; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
    <svg style="width: 24px; height: 24px; color: #3F51B5;" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
      <path d="M20 7l-8-4-8 4m16 0l-8 4m8-4v10l-8 4m0-10L4 7m8 4v10M4 7v10l8 4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
    </svg>
    Endereço de Entrega
  </p>
  <p style="margin: 6px 0; color: #555555; padding-left: 34px;">{{shippingAddress.street}}</p>
  <p style="margin: 6px 0; color: #555555; padding-left: 34px;">{{shippingAddress.city}}, {{shippingAddress.state}}</p>
  <p style="margin: 6px 0; color: #555555; padding-left: 34px;">CEP: {{shippingAddress.zipCode}}</p>
</div>
{{#if trackingUrl}}
<a href="{{trackingUrl}}" class="button">
  <svg style="display: inline-block; width: 18px; height: 18px; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 8px;" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
    <path d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
    <path d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
  </svg>
  Rastrear Pedido
</a>
{{/if}}
<div class="divider"></div>
<p style="color: #777777; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
  <svg style="width: 20px; height: 20px;" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
    <path d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
  </svg>
  <span>Você receberá uma notificação assim que seu pedido for enviado.</span>
</p>